          <div class="right-content">
            <p>We repair all major Danby residential freezer models, including:</p>
            <ul>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet" style="padding-left: 0 !important;" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" />Compact upright freezers such as <strong>Danby DUFM043A2WDD</strong> and <strong>DUFM085A4WDD</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet" style="padding-left: 0 !important;" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" />Chest freezers like <strong>DCF070A3WDB</strong> and <strong>DCF145A3WDB</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet" style="padding-left: 0 !important;" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" />Garage-ready models such as <strong>DCF072A3WDB</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet" style="padding-left: 0 !important;" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" />Mini freezers for apartments or dorm rooms including <strong>DCF038A2WDB-3</strong></li>
