          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>We provide flat-rate diagnostics, credited toward the repair if approved. Your cost includes:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">Genuine Danby parts and installation</li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">Certified EPA-compliant technician dispatch</li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">Office and insurance overhead</li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1"><strong>90-day warranty on all parts and labor</strong></li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">For more insight, visit our <a href="/price-list/freezer-repair-cost/" class="underline font-bold" style="color: #dc2626 !important;">Freezer Repair Cost Guide</a> to compare typical repair costs across brands.</p>
