        <div class="header-container">
          <div class="head-content-h">
            <h2>How Our Service Works</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>We make the repair process clear and stress-free:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] no-bullet pl-1">
                Book online or by phone before 3 PM for same-day arrival
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] no-bullet pl-1">
                Receive a technician profile and ETA
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] no-bullet pl-1">
