            <p>Whether you're dealing with ice buildup or inconsistent cooling, trust Same Day Appliance Repair to get your Danby freezer working like new. Book online at <a href="/services/refrigerator-repair-los-angeles/" class="underline font-bold" style="color: #dc2626 !important;">samedayappliance.repair</a> or call <strong>(323) 870‑4790</strong> for same-day service.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-container" id="anchor-12">
        <div class="header-container">
          <div class="head-content-h">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
